text: Kristina Kicka (born Kryszina Mikhailenko 26 March 1992 in Minsk) is a Belarusian volleyball player. She competed in the 2013–14 Women's CEV Cup, winning the gold medal with her team, Fenerbahçe S.K. == Clubs == Club From To Minchanka Minsk 2006-2007 2011-2012 LTS Legionovia Legionowo 2012-2013 2012-2013 Dresdner SC 2013-2014 2015-2016 İdmanocağı Spor Kulübü. 2016-2017 2016-2017 CSM Bucureşti.
